name: The Baddest Glitch
description: 820 x 1159 ; Miss me w/them parallels. Miss me w/logistics. Dismiss it if it make sense. Logic ain’t the remedy. Profits that make stability simplistic. Costs of living and expenses make the strings that limit your fluidity. A puppeteer. “Only up from here”. A couple beers. A drunk and a deer. Barely missed em by an inch.
